	* gst/gstelement.h:
	  remove gst_element_factory_get_version. It doesn't exist anymore.
	* gst/gstplugin.c:
	* gst/gstplugin.h:
	  remove gst_plugin_set_name and change gst_plugin_get_longname to
	  gst_plugin_get_description to match code.
